data.description: This charming single-family home in Krum, Texas, offers a cozy and inviting living space for families or an individual looking for a comfortable home. With three bedrooms and two bathrooms, this 1,226 square foot residence provides ample space for daily living and entertaining. The interior features a well-lit living room, a functional kitchen with modern appliances, and comfortable bedrooms. The property also boasts a spacious backyard with storage shed, perfect for outdoor activities and gardening. Situated in a peaceful neighborhood, this home provides a serene atmosphere while still being conveniently located near local amenities and schools. The property offers a great opportunity for homeownership in the welcoming community of Krum. Don't miss the chance to make this house your new home and experience the warmth and comfort it has to offer.
